version_description: I made corrections to chords and formatting to make it easier to get the timing of words
Tabbed in capo 1 for easier chords.
I couldn't find an accurate version of this song so I decided to make one myself.
The other tabs didn't have the correct chorus so I tried to make it better. This is standard tuning and not drop D but the loss of quality is minimal.
It has the actual lick tabbed that plays in the intro and verse. its the first one for this song. you can play it live following allong to my transcription.
Its most accurate and is tabbed in such a way so you can play it and follow along all the way thru.
It's based off how the electric guitar plays in the song itself. Doesn't use a capo.
